1
00:00:00,060 --> 00:00:02,900
[Episode 10]

2
00:00:00,060 --> 00:00:00,060
[Bangkok University]

3
00:00:04,430 --> 00:00:06,910
Hey, why did you choose
to study acting like me?

4
00:00:06,910 --> 00:00:08,790
Didn't you say you were going
to study digital technology?

5
00:00:08,790 --> 00:00:12,310
Because my brother told me
to cherish you like my own life.

6
00:00:12,590 --> 00:00:16,030
Small world, isn't it?

7
00:00:16,830 --> 00:00:18,150
Oh, Xi.

8
00:00:18,150 --> 00:00:21,870
Well, the lead is here.
Time for extras to step aside.

9
00:00:24,350 --> 00:00:25,420
Uh...

10
00:00:27,150 --> 00:00:28,550
How were you that day?

11
00:00:28,710 --> 00:00:31,070
You didn't even tell me
you had a boyfriend.

12
00:00:31,070 --> 00:00:35,030
Hey, that psycho put
a black plastic bag over my head.

13
00:00:35,030 --> 00:00:36,990
Then threw me into a wet garbage bin.

14
00:00:36,990 --> 00:00:37,990
Really?

15
00:00:38,790 --> 00:00:42,030
A black plastic bag over your head?
Is that really a thing?

16
00:00:42,590 --> 00:00:44,590
What on earth are you talking about?

17
00:00:45,590 --> 00:00:47,510
So... who is this?

18
00:00:48,230 --> 00:00:53,070
Ah, this is Fuchi, my relative.
He's half Japanese.

19
00:00:53,270 --> 00:00:58,340
Fuchi, this is Xi,
my middle school friend. He was the campus heartthrob.

20
00:00:58,870 --> 00:00:59,910
Hello.

21
00:01:03,390 --> 00:01:05,190
You two came at the perfect time.

22
00:01:06,070 --> 00:01:10,510
Right now, I'm planning...

23
00:01:11,390 --> 00:01:15,390
to shoot a cover photo
for the freshman magazine.

24
00:01:16,550 --> 00:01:19,270
What do you think? Interested?

25
00:01:20,789 --> 00:01:22,390
Volcano Boy.

26
00:01:24,670 --> 00:01:28,550
Hey, calm down.
He's a real man.

27
00:01:29,150 --> 00:01:30,940
A real man?

28
00:01:32,990 --> 00:01:34,870
Is there such a thing as fake men?

29
00:01:40,750 --> 00:01:42,110
Um, excuse me.

30
00:01:42,830 --> 00:01:45,070
Have you seen my friends
Xi and Fuchi?

31
00:01:45,229 --> 00:01:47,560
Oh, they're changing clothes backstage.

32
00:01:47,950 --> 00:01:49,390
Oh, thanks.

33
00:01:50,880 --> 00:01:52,000
Over there.

34
00:01:57,550 --> 00:01:59,470
Exciting! So exciting, bro!

35
00:02:03,670 --> 00:02:05,960
Hey, what are you doing?

36
00:02:06,420 --> 00:02:09,509
[To Be Continued]
